threepio.tabler.container
Class TRComponent

java.lang.Object
  threepio.tabler.container.TRComponent

public class TRComponent
extends java.lang.Object

TRComponent is a class that defines a Component from a BBF document. It is exclusively a container, with some constructors, getters, and setters.
